-- Carrefour seals deal to buy 127 Klepierre malls
-- By Maya Nikolaeva
-- Fri Jan 24, 2014 12:05PM EST
-- None



PARIS, Jan 24 (Reuters) - France's Carrefour <CARR.PA> said on Friday it signed a binding agreement with real estate group Klepierre <LOIM.PA> to buy a portfolio of 127 shopping malls in Europe, with the deal expected to close in the first half of 2014.

